{"tid":2505593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳遼寧號再擾台灣東外海 美單艦突入共軍航母戰鬥群編隊內","createTime":"2021-04-26T16:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T23:13:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b74a78ac3693afea8ca06f8b21c6de180c137935","tid":2505593,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/public/uploads/assets/2021/04/27/2021-04-27-6086e6fd93f17-460x258-169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F2021-04-27-6086e6fd93f17-460x258-169.jpg&h=ff804ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖/推特帳號OSINT-1<br />\n<br />\n專門監控軍艦動態的社群平台帳號OSINT-1在26日深夜推文顯示，中共遼寧號航空母艦戰鬥群，26日來到台灣東部外海的菲律賓海航行，並持續航向鄰近日本的宮古海峽, 不過，一艘美軍伯克級神盾驅逐艦，闖入共軍航母戰鬥群編隊內，持續監控遼寧號動向。<br />\n<br />\n在OSINT-1貼出的衛星照片中，6號是美軍神盾艦；1號紅框則是共軍遼寧號。<br />\n<br />\n美軍之前曾公布一張照片，馬斯廷號(Mustin)神盾艦，4月4日在台灣東部外海（菲律賓海），在目視距離內監控共軍遼寧號航母編隊，在網路引發熱議；後來傳出還有日本自衛隊艦艇也在附近監控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/public/uploads/assets/2021/04/27/2021-04-27-6086e7004ebbf-460x258-169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fpublic%2Fuploads%2Fassets%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F2021-04-27-6086e7004ebbf-460x258-169.jpg&h=2362124e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳遼寧號再擾台灣東外海 美艦單闖共軍艦隊追監（圖/推特帳號OSINT-1）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20210427/video/293893.html?傳遼寧號再擾台灣東外海%20美艦單闖共軍艦隊追監\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20210427%2Fvideo%2F293893.html%3F%E5%82%B3%E9%81%BC%E5%AF%A7%E8%99%9F%E5%86%8D%E6%93%BE%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%96%E6%B5%B7%2520%E7%BE%8E%E8%89%A6%E5%96%AE%E9%97%96%E5%85%B1%E8%BB%8D%E8%89%A6%E9%9A%8A%E8%BF%BD%E7%9B%A3&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=c041300a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20210427/video/293893.html?傳遼寧號再擾台灣東外海%20美艦單闖共軍艦隊追監</a>"},{"pid":"e90b6fd2d8e1e5c657542dfc5002c32c84f5c61b","tid":2505593,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"打!往死裏打!"},{"pid":"5824f04a550c6dc3a9da6704934c9b5c0f3a035f","tid":2505593,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"應該係經宮古海峽回港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49012ebe4fd35471c295b61d3b7acd3b49a9c196","tid":2505593,"uid":47810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"美帝係咪想跟到入港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c3385220314507e6fd62440fdb3d22a4ab45f6","tid":2505593,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"不如開咗炮先報啦，佢入唔入去冇人想知，比佢登陸埋都唔好開炮啦不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1988355a1eea20b3969f76ef8d7b75cfee919aba","tid":2505593,"uid":378134,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWA3hLorCRPSXGJ3g77bsxMBxNNnXahzuzGfFJpKjU3AL?filename=EX430nt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEX430nt.jpg&h=b1c2ae5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bdfcf7b1e192e89af838be2978034ca